    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>DHCP是动态主机配置协议. 这个协议用于向计算机自动提供IP地址,子网掩码和路由信息。网络管理员通常会分配某个范围的IP地址来分发给局域网上的客户机。当设备接入这个局域网时，它们会向 DHCP服务器请求一个 IP 地址。然后DHCP服务器为每个请求的设备分配一个地址，直到分配完该范围内的所有 IP 地址为止。已经分配的IP地址必须定时地延长借用期。这个延期的过程称作leasing，确保了当客户机设备在正常地释放IP地址之前突然从网络断开时被分配的地址可以归还给服务器。本文以Redhat Linux 5.5为例，介绍如何建立一个DHCP服务器。</p><blockquote><p>将IP设为静态IP地址</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi  /etc/sysconfig/network-scripts/ifcfg-eth0<span class="comment">#编辑网卡主配置文件,见下图</span></span><br><span class="line">service  network  restart<span class="comment">#重启网络服务</span></span><br><span class="line">ifconfig<span class="comment">#查看ip是否修改成</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div><img src="/images/dhcp1.png" alt=""></div><p><br></p><blockquote><p>安装dhcp程序包</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br><span class="line">4</span><br><span class="line">5</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">mkdir  /mnt/cdrom/</span><br><span class="line">mount  /dev/cdrom /mnt/cdrom/<span class="comment">#挂载镜像</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="built_in">cd</span>  /mnt/cdrom/Server/</span><br><span class="line">rpm  -ivh  dhcp-3.0.5-23.el5.i386.rpm<span class="comment">#安装</span></span><br><span class="line">rpm -qa dhcp<span class="comment">#查询是否安装成功</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br></p><blockquote><p>修改dhcp配置文件</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cp  /usr/share/doc/dhcp-3.0.5/dhcpd.conf.sample  /etc/dhcpd.conf<span class="comment">#把主配置文件拷贝到etc目录下，y 确定覆盖</span></span><br><span class="line">vi  /etc/dhcpd.conf<span class="comment">#编辑配置文件，见下图</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><div><img src="/images/dhcp2.png" alt=""></div><p><br></p><blockquote><p>关闭Selinux</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">vi  /etc/selinux/config</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><img src="/images/selinux.png" alt=""></p><p><br></p><blockquote><p>清空防火墙</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">iptables  -F</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br></p><blockquote><p>开启dhcp服务</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">service  dhcpd  start<span class="comment">#开启dhcp服务</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><p><br></p><blockquote><p>测试</p></blockquote><figure class="highlight bash"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br><span class="line">2</span><br><span class="line">3</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">将两台虚拟机设置为同一个虚拟网络</span><br><span class="line">ipconfig  /release<span class="comment">#释放IP地址</span></span><br><span class="line">ipconfig  /renew<span class="comment">#重新获取IP地址</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>]]></content>
    
